295
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,200
A bet is a bet.

296
00:13:37,639 --> 00:13:38,320
One hundred bucks.

297
00:13:40,279 --> 00:13:41,279
Hurry, hurry, hurry.

298
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:43,720
Bro Yong,

299
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:45,039
that's my dinner money.

300
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,879
I was gonna go eat KFC.

301
00:13:50,639 --> 00:13:52,440
Forget KFC.

302
00:13:53,720 --> 00:13:54,240
Tell you what,

303
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:56,759
Bro Yong will take you guys

304
00:13:57,279 --> 00:13:58,240
for a Chinese feast, how's that?

305
00:13:59,279 --> 00:14:00,559
Bro Yong's the man! Bro Yong's the man!

306
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:19,759
Come on, kids.

307
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:20,960
Have another drumstick.

308
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:22,080
Thanks, Auntie. Thank you.

309
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:23,120
It's nothing, nothing at all.

310
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:23,840
Eat up, okay?

311
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,799
Call me Bro Yong,

312
00:14:28,039 --> 00:14:29,360
and I'll give the money back.

313
00:14:29,559 --> 00:14:31,000
Bro Yong! Bro Yong!

314
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:34,799
Git gud!

315
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:44,519
Have some of this.

316
00:14:51,600 --> 00:14:52,000
What is it?

317
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:52,759
Something up?

318
00:14:54,759 --> 00:14:55,120
Mom,

319
00:14:57,879 --> 00:14:59,440
Coach Chang asked me to help him out

320
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:01,279
play in a small match.

321
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:05,919
You...

322
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:08,320
Is your leg up to it?

323
00:15:09,799 --> 00:15:10,159
Mom,

324
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:11,240
look, Mom,

325
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:12,440
I can do it.

326
00:15:14,799 --> 00:15:15,440
Well,

327
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:17,120
there's not much to do at the shop anyway.

328
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:19,360
So go ahead.

329
00:15:20,679 --> 00:15:21,080
Go on.

330
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:24,759
Alright, Mom!

331
00:16:46,559 --> 00:16:47,080
Coach.

332
00:16:48,279 --> 00:16:49,360
How's the family?

333
00:16:51,960 --> 00:16:52,399
Pretty good.

334
00:16:52,960 --> 00:16:53,679
Married yet?

335
00:16:56,440 --> 00:16:57,399
What do you do for work?

336
00:17:00,759 --> 00:17:01,440
No degree,

337
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:03,960
can't really land a good job.

338
00:17:07,920 --> 00:17:09,079
Five minutes late.

339
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:10,440
Coach,

340
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:12,200
I ran the whole way here.

341
00:17:12,279 --> 00:17:13,200
Is that an excuse?

342
00:17:14,079 --> 00:17:14,680
Same as always.

343
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:15,640
Five laps.
